==Swedish==
===Noun===
'''gång'''

#[[walk]], [[path]], [[trail]]; a maintained, quite narrow path on which to walk, which in general does not follow next to a road. (''Compare [[trottoar]]'').
#(''uncountable'') manner of [[walk]], [[gait]]
#{{sv-sports}} (''uncountable'') [[race walking]]
#the number of times something happens: 
#:''Han gjorde det inte en '''gång''', utan tre '''gånger''''' = ''He didn't do it '''once''', but '''thrice'''''.


